{"title": "Marie Antoinette Romances, Vol 3: The Queen's Necklace (Version 2)", "description": "This 3rd volume of the Marie Antoinette Romances begins a decade after the close of \"The Mesmerist\u2019s Victim\u201d and is based on a real scandal in Louis XVI\u2019s court, commonly called \u201cThe Diamond Necklace Affair.\u201d In this volume, the plotting of a powerful occultist, Count Cogliostro (or \u201cBalsamo\u201d), collides with the long-festering resentments of a previous royal house, Jeanne de Valois (de la Motte), a growing popular movement for sociopolitical reform, and a shrinking supply of bread. It is easy to see how converging sociopolitical challenges can threaten the monarchy, but how can the court of Louis XVI overcome these challenges amidst a famine? After all, in the words of his economic advisor, Turgot de l'Aulnes, \u201cNe vous m\u00ealez pas du pain\u201d (One must not meddle with bread)! - Summary by jvanstan", "duration": 60031, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "431", "name": "Alexandre Dumas"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/marieantoinette_3_2009_librivox/queens_necklace2_2009.jpg", "copyright_year": "1894", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction", "Crime & Mystery Fiction", "Fantastic Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "John Van Stan"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "John Van Stan"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Lynne T"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "pattymarie"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Prologue, The Predictions", "readers": [9017], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/marieantoinette_3_2009_librivox/marieantoinette3_01_dumas_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1185}, {"section": 2, "title": "Prologue, M. de la Perouse, Part 1", "readers": [9017], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/marieantoinette_3_2009_librivox/marieantoinette3_02_dumas_64kb.mp3", "duration": 2217}, {"section": 3, "title": "Prologue, M. de la Perouse, Part 2", "readers": [9017], "path": "ht